# Movement-cycle working area — captures, snapshots, smoke outputs, and any
# other transient dev-cycle data live here locally. The authoritative docs
# already tracked in this folder (orientation, deployment plan, work
# breakdown, movement packets, etc.) stay tracked — gitignore only affects
# untracked files, so existing committed docs continue to be diffable on the
# remote. Anything new dropped into this folder is silently ignored.
BUILD DOCS and DATA/
